defaultIn the present context, as well as embracing the concept of size, the word ʼscopeʼ
default 
defaultconnotes ʻrange of activitiesʼ and this raises a very serious and concerning aspect of
default 
defaultthe BBC in its present form.
default&#xa0;
defaultIn the BBC Charter one of the BB
defaultCʼs Public Purposes is ʻhelping to deliver to the
default 
defaultpublic the benefit of emerging communications technologiesʼ. In non-spin language
default 
